    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it really does feel like a prison. i look at people living normal lives and i just feel so disconnected. like i'm already gone, it's just my body that won't catch up. sometimes i think there's no point in fighting it anymore. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace.",
